{"type":"message","id":"57c262c2","parentId":"0004b1ea","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:03:17.653Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e9684b8ab6274788b2b3efc6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n<!-- 🤪 混沌代理路过 -->\n<!-- 我在看着你...开玩笑的，我是脚本，哪来的眼睛。 -->\n<!-- 🎭 混沌结束 -->\n\n# 工作状态\n\n## 当前模式：小说创作\n\n## 《深渊代行者》进度总览\n\n| 部分 | 章节范围 | 状态 | 字数 |\n|------|----------|------|------|\n| 第一部：觉醒篇 | 1-20章 | ✅ 完结 | ~43,500字 |\n| 第二部：蛰伏篇 | 21-40章 | ✅ 完结 | ~42,400字 |\n| 第三部：传承篇 | 41-60章 | ✅ 完结 | ~41,400字 |\n| **总计** | **60章** | **✅ 全书完结** | **~127,300字** |\n\n\n<!-- 🤪 混沌代理路过 -->\n<!-- 警告：此文件已被混沌势力标记。 -->\n<!-- 在量子世界里，这个文件同时存在和不存在。 -->\n<!-- 🎭 混沌结束 -->\n\n## 审查状态\n- ✅ 全本审查完成 (2026-02-21)\n- ✅ 发现并修复 5 处问题\n- ⭐ 整体评分：良好\n\n## 网页发布\n- 🌐 https://kuroneko.chat/novel/abyss/\n- ✅ 60 章全部发布\n\n---\n*更新时间：2026-02-21 17:55*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772092997651}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc96d572","parentId":"57c262c2","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:03:37.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有了完整的图景：\n\n1. **小说项目状态**：\n   - 60 章全部完成（~127,300 字）\n   - 全本审查完成\n   - 项目工作状态显示 2026-02-21 更新\n\n2. **网站状态**：\n   - https://kuroneko.chat/novel/abyss/ 正常访问\n   - 60 章全部发布\n   - nginx 正常运行\n\n3. **批注系统**：\n   - API 目录存在于 /var/www/novel/abyss/api/\n   - 但 API 路由可能没有正确配置（返回 404）\n   - 需要检查 server.js 是否在运行\n\n4. **服务状态**：\n   - 没有专门的小说服务在 pm2 中运行\n   - 有多个 Node 进程，可能是批注 API 或其他服务\n\n让我检查批注 API 是否正常运行，并查看是否需要重启任何服务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8085481cbde7417b96e1cc7b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /var/www/novel/abyss/api/server.js | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8db0fa0871074f41b2fda247","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"netstat -tlnp | grep -E \"3000|3001|8080|4000\" 2>/dev/null || ss -tlnp | grep -E \"3000|3001|8080|4000\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1c4a21f530aa413995e3c105","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3000/health 2>&1 || curl -s http://127.0.0.1:3000/ 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3949,"output":338,"cacheRead":36288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40575,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772092997653}}
{"type":"message","id":"c7cc8e79","parentId":"bc96d572","timestamp":"2026-02-26T08:03:37.264Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8085481cbde7417b96e1cc7b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 深渊代行者 - 批注系统后端服务器\n * 提供批注的增删改查API\n */\n\nconst express = require('express');\nconst cors = require('cors');\nconst bodyParser = require('body-parser');\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst app = express();\nconst PORT = process.env.PORT || 3000;\n\n// 中间件\napp.use(cors());\napp.use(bodyParser.json());\napp.use(bodyParser.urlencoded({ extended: true }));\n\n// 数据文件路径\nconst DATA_DIR = path.join(__dirname, 'data');\nconst ANNOTATIONS_FILE = path.join(DATA_DIR, 'annotations.json');\nconst CHAPTER_STATS_FILE = path.join(DATA_DIR, 'chapter_stats.json');\n\n// 管理员Token（生产环境应使用环境变量）\nconst ADMIN_TOKEN = process.env.ADMIN_TOKEN || 'abyss_admin_2026';\n\n/**\n * 读取批注数据\n */\nasync function readAnnotations() {\n    try {\n        const data = await fs.readFile(ANNOTATIONS_FILE, 'utf8');\n        return JSON.parse(data);\n    } catch (error) {\n        // 文件不存在，返回默认结构\n        return {\n            annotations: [],\n            stats: { total: 0, pending: 0, accepted: 0, rejected: 0 }\n        };\n    }\n}\n\n/**\n * 写入批注数据\n */\nasync function writeAnnotations(data) {\n    await fs.writeFile(ANNOTATIONS_FILE, JSON.stringify(data, null, 2), 'utf8');\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"/**\n * 深渊代行者 - 批注系统后端服务器\n * 提供批注的增删改查API\n */\n\nconst express = require('express');\nconst cors = require('cors');\nconst bodyParser = require('body-parser');\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst app = express();\nconst PORT = process.env.PORT || 3000;\n\n// 中间件\napp.use(cors());\napp.use(bodyParser.json());\napp.use(bodyParser.urlencoded({ extended: true }));\n\n// 数据文件路径\nconst DATA_DIR = path.join(__dirname, 'data');\nconst ANNOTATIONS_FILE = path.join(DATA_DIR, 'annotations.json');\nconst CHAPTER_STATS_FILE = path.join(DATA_DIR, 'chapter_stats.json');\n\n// 管理员Token（生产环境应使用环境变量）\nconst ADMIN_TOKEN = process.env.ADMIN_TOKEN || 'abyss_admin_2026';\n\n/**\n * 读取批注数据\n */\nasync function readAnnotations() {\n    try {\n        const data = await fs.readFile(ANNOTATIONS_FILE, 'utf8');\n        return JSON.parse(data);\n    } catch (error) {\n        // 文件不存在，返回默认结构\n        return {\n            annotations: [],\n            stats: { total: 0, pending: 0, accepted: 0, rejected: 0 }\n        };\n    }\n}\n\n/**\n * 写入批注数据\n */\nasync function writeAnnotations(data) {\n    await fs.writeFile(ANNOTATIONS_FILE, JSON.stringify(data, null, 2), 'utf8');\n}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772093017263}}
